                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": "<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"width-750-pixels\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\" class=\"width-40-pixels\">Stap 1              <img alt=\"\" src=\"https://maken.wikiwijs.nl/userfiles/d/da8b021b65aaebe06615f66ff836e15f3312639e.PNG\" class=\"height-164-pixels width-400-pixels\"/></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\">Stap 2               <img alt=\"\" src=\"https://maken.wikiwijs.nl/userfiles/e/e0fe2188a2d4c0f74178a2217eac37b025b5d067.PNG\" class=\"height-138-pixels width-400-pixels\"/></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\">Stap 3               <img alt=\"\" src=\"https://maken.wikiwijs.nl/userfiles/9/911cc99fdda3d51874694bfe4d496a28de2d87f4.PNG\" class=\"height-141-pixels width-400-pixels\"/></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\">Stap 4              <img alt=\"\" src=\"https://maken.wikiwijs.nl/userfiles/6/68ef409e9ad7f7058faac04b8d07d78f20ec3906.PNG\" class=\"height-278-pixels width-400-pixels\"/></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\">Stap 5                 <img alt=\"\" src=\"https://maken.wikiwijs.nl/userfiles/6/6c539d1d9ea91ef8a8f1986c4f52a4c177386bd8.PNG\" class=\"height-249-pixels width-400-pixels\"/></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\">Stap 6                    <img alt=\"\" src=\"https://maken.wikiwijs.nl/userfiles/7/7f650449c5676a69836d77816f654887fd65e365.PNG\" class=\"height-197-pixels width-400-pixels\"/></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\">Stap 7                 <img alt=\"\" src=\"https://maken.wikiwijs.nl/userfiles/2/27e1bc59403f9c65f7e40559384e5529c8e94e3d.PNG\" class=\"height-201-pixels width-400-pixels\"/></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Stap 8                <img alt=\"\" src=\"https://maken.wikiwijs.nl/userfiles/b/bc1b7ea432ea743706fe7feb01f7e31eeae30eaa.PNG\" class=\"height-192-pixels width-400-pixels\"/></td>\n<td> </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p> </p>\n"
